FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our food delivery app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I place an order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse restaurants, select your items, add them to cart, and proceed to checkout. Choose your payment method and confirm your delivery address.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on distance and restaurant. You can view the exact fee before placing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times depend on distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation. You'll see an estimated delivery time before confirming your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can track your order in real-time through our app once it's been picked up by the delivery driver.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How do I contact customer support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: You can reach our customer support team through the app's help section, or by emailing support@fooddeliveryapp.com.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants and delivers food straight to your door. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your delivery in real-time.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary based on distance and restaurant. You'll see the exact fee before completing your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times depend on factors like distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation. On average, most orders arrive within 30-45 minutes. You can track your order's progress in the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I schedule orders in advance?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes! You can schedule orders up to 7 days in advance. This is perfect for planning meals or ensuring you have food ready for a specific time or event.
